                Dabis Aninio Moderato <lb n="2"/>militi <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> XXI rapacis <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr><am><g type="centuria"/></am></abbr><ex>centuria</ex></expan> Vindicis
